---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Donate | Digestive Harmony"
  description="Support Digestive Harmony and help advance hope, education, awareness, and community for people affected by IBD."
>
  <main>
    <section class="donate-hero">
      <img class="decor hero-leaf" src="/leaf-pattern.png" alt="" />
      <img class="decor hero-butterfly" src="/butterfly-icon.png" alt="" />

      <p class="eyebrow">Donate</p>
      <h1>Your support helps bring hope to families affected by IBD.</h1>
      <p>
        Every gift helps Digestive Harmony create trusted resources, raise awareness,
        and support individuals and families navigating Crohn’s disease, ulcerative colitis,
        and digestive health challenges.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="impact">
      <h2>Your Gift Supports</h2>
      <div class="small-line"></div>

      <div class="cards">
        <article>
          <h3>Education</h3>
          <p>Clear, compassionate resources that help patients and families understand IBD.</p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <h3>Awareness</h3>
          <p>Community outreach that helps reduce stigma and increase understanding.</p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <h3>Support</h3>
          <p>Programs and resources that remind patients and caregivers they are not alone.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="donation-box">
      <div>
        <p class="cta-label">Make a Difference</p>
        <h2>Donate to Digestive Harmony</h2>
        <p>
          Online donations will be available soon. Until then, please contact us if you
          would like to support Digestive Harmony or discuss giving opportunities.
        </p>
      </div>

      <a href="mailto:info@digestiveharmony.org">Contact Us to Donate</a>
    </section>

    <section class="note">
      <h2>Thank you for believing in this mission.</h2>
      <p>
        Your generosity helps us build a community rooted in education, compassion,
        awareness, and hope.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .donate-hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 105px 8% 115px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 12% 78%, rgba(110,66,193,.14), transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 88% 20%, rgba(6,152,168,.12), transparent 32%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #fbf7ff 45%, #ecfbfc);
  }

  .donate-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(56px, 7vw, 88px);
    line-height: .98;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 14px 0 20px;
  }

  .donate-hero p:last-child {
    max-width: 850px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 21px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--purple);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .2em;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .hero-leaf {
    width: 360px;
    left: -90px;
    bottom: -70px;
    opacity: .08;
  }

  .hero-butterfly {
    width: 88px;
    right: 8%;
    top: 80px;
    opacity: .18;
  }

  .impact {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 76px 6%;
  }

  .impact h2,
  .note h2 {
    font-size: 46px;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .small-line {
    width: 76px;
    height: 4px;
    margin: 14px auto 44px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--purple), var(--teal));
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 26px;
  }

  article {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 40px 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    border: 1px solid #edf1f7;
  }

  article h3 {
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }

  article p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .donation-box {
    margin: 20px 6% 74px;
    padding: 64px;
    border-radius: 34px;
    color: white;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 86% 35%, rgba(255,255,255,.14), transparent 28%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--teal));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 36px;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 54px rgba(8,41,79,.16);
  }

  .cta-label {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .16em;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 900;
    opacity: .9;
  }

  .donation-box h2 {
    max-width: 760px;
    font-size: 44px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }

  .donation-box p {
    max-width: 760px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .donation-box a {
    background: white;
    color: var(--purple);
    padding: 17px 36px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 900;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .note {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 8% 90px;
  }

  .note p {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 18px auto 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .donation-box {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 44px 26px;
    }

    .hero-leaf,
    .hero-butterfly {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
